ikaaro 0.62.7 (2011/03/28)
==========================

This is a Content Management System built on Python & itools, among
other features ikaaro provides:

 - content and document management (index&search, metadata, etc.)
 - multilingual user interfaces and content
 - high level modules: wiki, forum, tracker, etc.

Changes
-------

NOTE: when upgrading to this new version it is recommended to run
icms-update-catalog.py; two new indexes have been added to improve
the performance of some queries, while they are not yet used they
will in the next version. See bug #605 for details.

Features:
- Now from the "Browse content" view it is possible to download a ZIP
  archive with the selected files (bug #1189)

User interface:
- More beautiful icons
- Do not show users in the "Browse Content" view

Performance improvements:
- Optimize 'get_revisions' for the root resource
- Use an sprite for the sort icons

Access control
- Now the user profile is not visible to anonymous users when the
  website is in 'intranet' mode (bug #1185)

Submodules
- Calendar: many improvements and fixes (#1176, #1177, #1178, #1184)
- Tracker: add link to download a ZIP file with the attachments

Translations
- Update French translations


